QuestData.Title: The Call of Kalimdor
QuestData.Description: I've been sent by the good people of Theramore to find loyal members of the Alliance who are willing to help Lady Jaina with some problems in Dustwallow.$b$bYou weren't really here working for the goblins, were you?$b$bThe path back to Dustwallow will take you through Ratchet. Wait on the end of this pier for the next boat. Once you get to Ratchet, speak with Gazlowe. He'll point you in the right direction from there.$b$bUgh, I think I stepped on a fish! And it flopped!
QuestData.LogDescription: Ride the ship from Booty Bay to Ratchet, then speak with Gazlowe.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Report to Gazlowe at Ratchet in the Northern Barrens.
